com.gdxgame.core.enums

Enum SoundType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SoundType>
      • com.gdxgame.core.enums.SoundType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SoundType>

    public enum SoundType
extends Enum<SoundType>
    SoundType enum is the configuration enum for sound that is used for the game. Each value contains the path to the sound file.
